 CBGridVsNuGrid args;id;eventName;logMsg;currentLog;row;col;mouseFlag;newValue;source
‚çù Event callback for Grid vs NuGrid comparison demo
‚çù Logs events with source label (Grid or NuGrid)

 id‚Üê‚äÉargs
 eventName‚Üê2‚äÉargs

‚çù Identify which grid fired the event
 source‚Üê(1+‚à®/'NG'‚ç∑id)‚äÉ'Grid' 'NuGrid'

‚çù Format the event message
 :Select eventName
 :Case 'CellMove'
     row‚Üê3‚äÉargs
     col‚Üê4‚äÉargs
     mouseFlag‚Üê7‚äÉargs
     logMsg‚Üê'[',(source),'] CellMove: Row ',(‚çïrow),' Col ',(‚çïcol),(mouseFlag=0)/' (kbd)'
     logMsg,‚Üê(mouseFlag=1)/' (click)'
 :Case 'CellChanged'
     row‚Üê3‚äÉargs
     col‚Üê4‚äÉargs
     newValue‚Üê5‚äÉargs
     logMsg‚Üê'[',(source),'] CellChanged: [',(‚çïrow),',',(‚çïcol),'] = ',‚çïnewValue
 :Else
     logMsg‚Üê'[',(source),'] ',eventName,': ',‚çï2‚Üìargs
 :EndSelect

‚çù Prepend to event log
 currentLog‚Üê'F1.Log'eWG'Caption'
 'F1.Log'eWS'Caption'(logMsg,(‚éïUCS 10),currentLog)
